&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_17n failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;rm: cannot remove `/mnt/lustre/d17n.sanity/remote_dir_0&apos;: Stale file handle&lt;br/&gt;
destroy remote dir error 0&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanity 17n&lt;/p&gt;</description>
